<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 06:15:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>农化公司先正达第一季度销售额和盈利大幅下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/agrochemicals-company-syngenta-posts-big-drop-q1-sales-earnings-2024-04-29/</link><description>种子和农药制造商先正达周一表示，第一季度销售额和利润大幅下降，就在这家瑞士公司搁置其 100 亿美元上市计划几周后。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 06:08:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/agrochemicals-company-syngenta-posts-big-drop-q1-sales-earnings-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国四月份工厂活动扩张速度可能放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-april-factory-activity-likely-expanded-slower-speed-2024-04-29/</link><description>路透社周一的一项调查显示，中国四月份的制造业活动可能会放缓，这表明该国庞大的工厂部门可能在第二季度初失去了一些动力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:49:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-april-factory-activity-likely-expanded-slower-speed-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产股因刺激计划而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-property-shares-rally-stimulus-hopes-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国房地产开发商的股价周一上涨，因市场猜测本周可能会出台更多刺激措施，旨在清理库存、促进销售和取消购房限制。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:47:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-property-shares-rally-stimulus-hopes-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，台湾经济第一季度因出口强劲而增长5.6%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwans-economy-seen-expanding-56-first-quarter-strong-exports-2024-04-29/</link><description>路透社周一的一项民意调查显示，由于对人工智能（AI）应用技术的需求乐观，出口反弹，台湾依赖贸易的经济可能在第一季度增长更快。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:03:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwans-economy-seen-expanding-56-first-quarter-strong-exports-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，百度与特斯拉就 FSD 在中国的地图绘制交易达成一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-tesla-agree-mapping-deal-fsd-china-sources-say-2024-04-29/</link><description>两位知情人士称，中国主要互联网搜索公司百度与特斯拉达成协议，授予该汽车公司在中国公共道路上收集数据的测绘许可证。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 04:24:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-tesla-agree-mapping-deal-fsd-china-sources-say-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>彭博新闻社称，特斯拉与百度的交易扫清了中国辅助驾驶领域的关键障碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tesla-clears-key-china-assisted-driving-hurdle-with-baidu-deal-bloomberg-news-2024-04-29/</link><description>据彭博社周一报道，特斯拉将通过与百度合作开发地图和导航功能，扫清在中国推出先进辅助驾驶功能的关键障碍。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 04:14:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tesla-clears-key-china-assisted-driving-hurdle-with-baidu-deal-bloomberg-news-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产开发商佳兆业清算听证会延期至5月27日</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-property-developer-kaisas-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-may-27-2024-04-29/</link><description>香港一家法院将佳兆业集团清算听证会推迟至 5 月 27 日，这家陷入困境的中国房地产开发商表示，其目标是在未来 4 周内敲定重组条款。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 03:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-property-developer-kaisas-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-may-27-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国将向月球“隐藏”的一面发起高风险任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-set-launch-high-stakes-mission-moons-hidden-side-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国将在未来几天内发射一艘机器人航天器往返月球背面，这是三项技术要求很高的任务中的第一项，这将为中国首次载人登陆和在月球南极建立基地铺平道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 03:23:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-set-launch-high-stakes-mission-moons-hidden-side-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>马斯克访华期间，特斯拉扫清了自动驾驶在中国的关键监管障碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/boss-battery-giant-catl-visits-elon-musks-hotel-beijing-reuters-witness-2024-04-29/</link><description>特斯拉已经清除了一些长期阻碍其在中国推出自动驾驶软件的关键监管障碍，为埃隆·马斯克出人意料地访问这家美国汽车制造商第二大市场并取得良好成果铺平了道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 03:06:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/boss-battery-giant-catl-visits-elon-musks-hotel-beijing-reuters-witness-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>日元因疑似干预而飙升，亚洲股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-29/</link><description>日元兑其他货币周一大幅上涨，此前日元兑美元汇率在盘中早些时候跌破 160 美元，引发人们猜测日本可能在日本度假期间干预货币市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 02:39:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商旭辉重组计划获得债券持有人批准</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-developer-cifi-gets-bondholder-nod-debt-restructuring-plan-2024-04-29/</link><description>陷入困境的中国房地产开发商旭辉控股周一表示，已与一批关键债券持有人就海外债务重组计划达成协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 02:27:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-developer-cifi-gets-bondholder-nod-debt-restructuring-plan-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>华为支持的 Aito 电动汽车在中国发生事故，造成三人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/huawei-suv-crash-kills-three-chinas-shanxi-province-says-state-media-2024-04-29/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，一辆华为支持的 Aito M7 SUV 在中国北部山西省运城市的高速公路上与一辆卡车相撞后起火，造成三人死亡，其中包括一名两岁男孩。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 01:14:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/huawei-suv-crash-kills-three-chinas-shanxi-province-says-state-media-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>独家：随着银行撤回，中国公司在俄罗斯付款方面转入“地下”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-firms-go-underground-russia-payments-banks-pull-back-2024-04-28/</link><description>随着中国大银行退出对俄罗斯相关交易的融资，一些中国企业开始转向边境小银行和货币经纪人等地下融资渠道，甚至禁止加密货币。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 23:22:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-firms-go-underground-russia-payments-banks-pull-back-2024-04-28/</guid></item><item><title>保险公司友邦保险 (AIA) 第一季​​度新业务价值增长 31%，宣布回购 20 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/insurer-aias-first-quarter-new-business-value-rises-31-announces-2-billion-2024-04-28/</link><description>总部位于香港的保险公司友邦保险集团周一公布，由于各业务部门的强劲表现，其第一季度新业务价值（VONB）按固定汇率计算增长了 31%，并宣布额外回购 20 亿美元的股票。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 22:13:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/insurer-aias-first-quarter-new-business-value-rises-31-announces-2-billion-2024-04-28/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：日元乱七八糟，美国科技补剂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-28/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 21:46:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>